Parameters: The result from the API call. May not be null.

Some result types may implement @B_com#google#android#gms#common#api#Releasable_E@, in which case @B_com#google#android#gms#common#api#Releasable#release_E@ should be used to free the associated resources. This method is called on the main thread, unless overridden by {GoogleApiClient.Builder#setHandler}.

ClassDesc: An interface for receiving a @B_com#google#android#gms#common#api#Result_E@ from a @B_com#google#android#gms#common#api#PendingResult_E@ as an asynchronous callback.
